data.description: Please do not sleep on this beautiful ranch. Warm colors throughout, spacious 3 bedrooms on the main floor and 1 bedroom in the lower level, 2 full baths and an open kitchen. Sliders to a nice size deck overlooking the back yard. Lower level also has a family room and office area. The seller has requested showings only on Saturday's and Sunday's due to the vigorous weekly schedule. So please send your requests for Saturday between 11 and 7 and Sunday between 12 and 5, thank you for your understanding.
